Notes: well here we are again, this time, all this is a re-encode of the russian
release which seems to be from a spanish source. as with most cams, taken from the
side, has movement this release already has someones filters being used and ben
worked over.

work that needed done, rotated, croped, bit of the ol' perspective to straighten out
and level off best we can. while not a lot of noise and some decent detail, there
were parts that the saturation needed some attention. brought those down, tweaked
rgb &amp; a splash of sharpness to bring back some of the detail due to the loss using
a de-noiser.

** reason why mostly to read nfo - - throughout the movie there are some hot spots
and a few places where the whites are off the hook.you notice the worst about 3/4 of
the way through. &quot;you have been warned&quot; -  audio is from a special friend and we are
greatful for the hook up. it's amazing sounding for what it is. . .

